npm start
files gets hosted on the localmachine
and you access this way: localhost:3000/home
machinename:PORTNAME/routeName

Hosting 
when you deploy(copy) your files to remote client/system
your files get copied to a remote system
remoteSystemURL/routeName

remoteSystemURL/ --> remoteSystemURL/default route

www.facebook.com --> facebook.com/home

DNS mapping


npm install -g firebase-tools
firebase login
firebase init
ng build --prod
firebase deploy


